A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. A startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session. As the event progresses, announcement chimes signal the final hour of the fair, while small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic. Once the fair concludes, students exit the gym carrying tote bags filled with branded notebooks and pens, as well as a stack of business cards provided by the recruiters.

A whiteboard lists employers scheduling same-day interviews, and career center staff log attendance metrics on laptops. Human resources teams jot notes on tablets as students introduce themselves, while some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. Additionally, students use tablets at kiosks to upload resumes to the fair database, and a data science company showcases a live dashboard displaying fair attendance. Small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic, and a startup founder invites students to a lunchtime pitch session.

Small groups analyze which recruiters seemed most enthusiastic, and some students rehearse elevator pitches quietly against the wall. In addition, healthcare providers showcase community outreach photos. Meanwhile, international students queue for advice on visa sponsorship requirements outside the university gym before the career fair opens.
